data.description: Introducing Your Dream Country Estate in Georgia! Nestled in the heart of Georgias Piedmont, this 2-story, 4-bedroom, 2-full bath home is a rustic yet modern haven. Featuring quartz countertops and a spacious kitchen with dual fridges and a deep basin sink, this home is perfect for those who are in search of a Country Estate, High end Hunting Camp or a Corporate getaway. Step into the generous living space and gaze out at the sprawling, well-maintained yard thats perfect for enjoying all this seldom offered type property has to offer. Upstairs, youll find a bedroom and two flex space rooms, offering endless possibilities for customization. This property isnt just a home; its an ideal country estate. With a capacity to accommodate over 8 guests, its a corporate lodge dream come true. Plus, the two outbuildings a 30x25 pole barn for storage and a 42x50 shop with power, water, and a roll-up garage door and ability to exhibit phase 3 power makes it perfect for any project with a multitude of uses. Dont worry about power outages; this property comes with an independent generator for those looking for sustainability, Inside, enjoy the elegance of a formal dining area, complete with an electric built-in fireplace in the spacious living room. Pine walls in the hallway foyer add to the rustic charm. Outdoors, youll discover a 1-acre lake stocked with Bass, Crappie, Catfish, and Gizzard Shad to keep game fish well-fed. With mature hardwoods, extensive internal road systems, two creeks, and strategically placed deer stands, (1 being a 4-person Box stand) this is a hunters paradise. Theres even Persimmon trees, bait station, and muscadine patch in view of the 4-man box stand and an ideal Archery stand. Less than an hour from the Ritz Carlton on Lake Oconee, 50 minutes from Athens, 1 hour 15 minutes from Atlanta, and under an hour from Augusta, this property offers both Privacy and accessibility. This country estate is your gateway to a Georgia beauty, a world-class retreat or your own Rural estate. Dont miss out on this incredible opportunity to live the dream. Act now and make this piece of Georgia paradise your own! Call today for a driven tour of the property and view all this property has to offer!
